BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Appeals Committee
DTSTART:20260625T170000Z
DTEND:20260625T210000Z
DTSTAMP:20260607T083332Z
UID:285154ff-21cb-5de8-b39b-33f4256f0b4f
DESCRIPTION:The Burlington Appeals Committee is an administrative tribunal
  established by City Council in August 2025 (DGM-57-25).  The Appeals C
 ommittee hears appeals from decisions issued by the City related to it’s
  Licensing By-laws.  It also hears appeals from orders issued by the City
  related to it’s Property Standards By-law. The Appeals Committee makes 
 final decisions that are not reviewed by City Council.\n\nDetails: https:/
 /events.burlington.ca/meetings/Detail/2026-06-25-1300-Appeals-Committee
URL:https://events.burlington.ca/meetings/Detail/2026-06-25-1300-Appeals-C
 ommittee
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
